CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 2, 1954, pg. 12, reads: "THE DECKS GIVE A PARTY - The popular young maids and matron club group, the Decks, gave their annual Christmas cocktail party at Loendi Club, Sunday evening, for some three hundred friends. Snapped during the gay evening by Photographer Teenie Harris are... Center photo: Cornelia Kinsey and Mozelle Thompson of New York City, and Phyllis Garland of McKeesport, home for the holidays from Northwestern University... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Decks Club members Cornelia Kinsey and Phyllis Garland standing on either side of artist Mozelle Thompson, in Loendi Club for Christmas party
